OL,6,FA knife used in a school stabbing that
OL,7,Finjured two teachers and a pupil was
OL,8,Fowned by the defendant's father, a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.
OL,11,FTeachers Fiona Elias, Liz Hopkin and a
OL,12,Fyear 10 pupil were stabbed during an
OL,13,Fattack at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman in April
OL,14,F2024.
OL,16,FA 14-year-old girl denies three counts
OL,17,Fof attempted murder after admitting
OL,18,Fthree counts of wounding with intent
OL,19,Fand a charge of possessing a bladed
OL,20,Farticle on school premises.
