OL,3,CKnife used in Ammanford stabbing
OL,4,Cbelonged to girl's father
OL,6,FThe father of the teenage girl told a
OL,7,Fjury that he used the multi-tool knife
OL,8,Ffor fishing and kept the knife among
OL,9,Fhis fishing equipment.
OL,11,FIn the weeks leading up to the attack,
OL,12,Fthe father said he had used the knife
OL,13,Fwhile decorating the family home and
OL,14,Fhad left it in the dining room.
OL,16,FThe court heard the father had agreed
OL,17,Fto check his daughter's bag each
OL,18,Fmorning after the girl was caught with
OL,19,Fa knife in school in the months before
OL,20,Fthe attack.
