OL,3,CKnife used in Ammanford stabbing
OL,4,Cbelonged to girl's father
OL,6,FHowever, on the morning of the
OL,7,Fstabbings he had failed to check his
OL,8,Fdaughter's belongings before she left
OL,9,Ffor school.
OL,11,FHe told the court "I hadn't checked my
OL,12,Ffishing gear for a good couple of
OL,13,Fweeks."
OL,15,FAsked if he had noticed the knife had
OL,16,Fbeen taken on the day of the attack he
OL,17,Fsaid "No, I hadn't seen it missing,
OL,18,Fnot until the afternoon unfortunately."
