OL,6,FThe witness described how the knife
OL,7,Fhad a locking mechanism that was
OL,8,Fengaged when the handle and blade were
OL,9,Fclosed together. "To open the blade
OL,10,Ftakes effort, you have to pull it out
OL,11,Fwhen it's locked," he said.
OL,13,FThe court heard the defendant had only
OL,14,Frecently moved to Ysgol Dyffryn Aman
OL,15,Fafter moving from Ysgol Maes Y
OL,16,FGwendraeth.
