OL,4,Cbelonged to girl's father
OL,6,FDuring cross-examination, the father
OL,7,Fsaid his daughter had suffered
OL,8,Fbullying at both schools while
OL,9,Ftravelling on the school bus and while
OL,10,Fwalking home.
OL,12,FHe also told how the family home had
OL,13,Fbeen targeted with eggs just weeks
OL,14,Fbefore the stabbing attack.
OL,16,F"Bullying had the biggest effect on
OL,17,Fher at that period, sometimes she
OL,18,Fwould isolate herself from things," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
